{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Grid Areas","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Glossary/Grid_Areas","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>Um &nbsp;<strong>grid area&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;é um ou mais <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Cell\">grid cells <small>(en-US)</small></a>&nbsp;que compõem uma área retangular do grid.&nbsp; As Grid Areas quando se&nbsp;coloca um item &nbsp;usando&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Line-based_Placement_with_CSS_Grid\">line-based placement</a>&nbsp;(posicionamento baseado em colunas e linha)ou quando define áreas usando&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Grid_Template_Areas\">named grid areas</a>(substituindo o nome).</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"Image showing a highlighted grid area\" src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/14771/1_Grid_Area.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n\n<p>Áreas do Grid devem ser de natureza regutangular; não é possível criar por exemplo&nbsp;uma área de grid em&nbsp;forma de T ou L&nbsp;.</p>\n\n<p>No exemplo abaixo temos um grid contêiner com dois items de grid, nomeamos esses com a propriedade <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-area\"><code>grid-area</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> e em seguida colocamos eles no&nbsp;grid usando&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\"><code>grid-template-areas</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. Isso &nbsp;cria duas áreas de grid, uma cobrindo 4 áreas do grid e a&nbsp;outra duas áreas do grid.</p>\n\n<div id=\"example_1\">\n\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">.wrapper</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-template-columns</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>3<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>1fr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-template-rows</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-template-areas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"a a b\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"a a b\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.item1</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-area</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> a<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.item2</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-area</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> b<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>wrapper<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n   <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>item1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Item<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n   <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>item2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Item<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"example 1 sample\" id=\"frame_example_1\" width=\"300\" height=\"280\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/pt-BR/docs/Glossary/Grid_Areas/_sample_.example_1.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"saiba_mais","title":"Saiba Mais","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"property_reference","title":"Property reference","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\"><code>grid-template-columns</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\"><code>grid-template-rows</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\"><code>grid-auto-rows</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\"><code>grid-auto-columns</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\"><code>grid-template-areas</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-area\"><code>grid-area</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"further_reading","title":"Further reading","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>CSS Grid Layout Guide: <em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Basic_Concepts_of_Grid_Layout\">Basic concepts of grid layout</a></em></li>\n <li>CSS Grid Layout Guide: <em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Grid_Template_Areas\">Grid template areas</a></em></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-grid/#grid-area-concept\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Definition of Grid Areas in the CSS Grid Layout specification</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Saiba Mais","id":"saiba_mais"}],"summary":"Um  grid area  é um ou mais grid cells (en-US) que compõem uma área retangular do grid.  As Grid Areas quando se coloca um item  usando line-based placement (posicionamento baseado em colunas e linha)ou quando define áreas usando named grid areas(substituindo o nome).","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Grid Areas","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Grid Areas","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Zone de grille","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Grid エリア","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Grid Areas","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/glossary/grid_areas","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/glossary/grid_areas/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Glossary","title":"Glossário"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Glossary/Grid_Areas","title":"Grid Areas"}],"pageTitle":"Grid Areas - Glossário | MDN","noIndexing":false}}